<style>
  .batlle-biography {
    padding: 9rem 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .batlle-biography__layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 990px) {
    .batlle-biography__layout {
      grid-template-columns: 5fr 7fr;
      gap: 4rem;
    }

    .batlle-biography__portrait-col {
      order: 1;
    }

    .batlle-biography__content-col {
      order: 2;
    }
  }

  .batlle-biography__portrait-col {
    position: relative;
  }

  .batlle-biography__frame {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 20rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .batlle-biography__frame-border {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.4);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .batlle-biography__frame-image {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .batlle-biography__frame-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .batlle-biography__name-badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -1.25rem;
    right: -1.25rem;
    background: rgb(var(--color-foreground));
    color: rgb(var(--color-background));
    padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .batlle-biography__supertitle {
    font-family: var(--font-body-family);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .batlle-biography__title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family);
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    line-height: 1;
    font-weight: var(--font-heading-weight);
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    color: rgb(var(--color-foreground));
  }

  .batlle-biography__title em {
    font-weight: var(--font-heading-weight);
  }

  .batlle-biography__body {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.7);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    max-width: 32rem;
  }

  .batlle-biography__body p {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .batlle-biography__body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .batlle-biography__skills {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    padding-top: 2.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.15);
    max-width: 32rem;
  }

  .batlle-biography__skill-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body-family);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(var(--color-foreground), 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .batlle-biography__skill-value {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family);
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    color: rgb(var(--color-foreground));
  }

  /* Phone ≤749px */
  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .batlle-biography {
      padding: 5rem 0;
    }

    .batlle-biography__layout {
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .batlle-biography__frame {
      max-width: 16rem;
    }

    .batlle-biography__frame-border {
      inset: -0.75rem;
    }

    .batlle-biography__name-badge {
      bottom: -1rem;
      right: -1rem;
      padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .batlle-biography__supertitle {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .batlle-biography__title {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3rem);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .batlle-biography__body {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .batlle-biography__skills {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 1.2rem;
      padding-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .batlle-biography__skill-label {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }

    .batlle-biography__skill-value {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }
  }

  /* Tablet 750–989px */
  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) and (max-width: 989px) {
    .batlle-biography {
      padding: 6rem 0;
    }

    .batlle-biography__layout {
      grid-template-columns: 6fr 6fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .batlle-biography__frame {
      max-width: 18rem;
    }

    .batlle-biography__name-badge {
      font-size: 1.7rem;
      padding: 0.7rem 1.3rem;
      bottom: -1rem;
      right: -1rem;
    }

    .batlle-biography__title {
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .batlle-biography__body {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .batlle-biography__skills {
      gap: 1.5rem;
      padding-top: 2rem;
    }

    .batlle-biography__skill-value {
      font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2vw, 1.8rem);
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="batlle-biography color-{{ section.settings.color_scheme }} gradient" id="batlle-louise">
  <div class="page-width">
    <div class="batlle-biography__layout">
      <div class="batlle-biography__portrait-col{% if settings.animations_reveal_on_scroll %} scroll-trigger animate--slide-in{% endif %}">
        <div class="batlle-biography__frame">
          <div class="batlle-biography__frame-border" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="batlle-biography__frame-image">
            {%- if section.settings.portrait != blank -%}
              {%- assign img_h = section.settings.portrait.width | divided_by: section.settings.portrait.aspect_ratio -%}
              {{
                section.settings.portrait
                | image_url: width: 600
                | image_tag:
                  width: section.settings.portrait.width,
                  height: img_h,
                  sizes: '(min-width: 990px) 40vw, 80vw',
                  widths: '375, 550, 750',
                  loading: 'lazy'
              }}
            {%- else -%}
              {{ 'image' | placeholder_svg_tag: 'placeholder-svg' }}
            {%- endif -%}
          </div>
          {%- if section.settings.name_badge != blank -%}
            <div class="batlle-biography__name-badge">{{ section.settings.name_badge }}</div>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="batlle-biography__content-col{% if settings.animations_reveal_on_scroll %} scroll-trigger animate--slide-in{% endif %}">
        {%- if section.settings.supertitle != blank -%}
          <p class="batlle-biography__supertitle">{{ section.settings.supertitle }}</p>
        {%- endif -%}
        {%- if section.settings.title != blank -%}
          <h2 class="batlle-biography__title">{{ section.settings.title }}</h2>
        {%- endif -%}
        {%- if section.settings.body != blank -%}
          <div class="batlle-biography__body">
            {{ section.settings.body }}
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}

        {%- if section.settings.skill_1_value != blank or section.settings.skill_2_value != blank or section.settings.skill_3_value != blank -%}
          <dl class="batlle-biography__skills">
            {%- if section.settings.skill_1_value != blank -%}
              <div>
                <dt class="batlle-biography__skill-label">{{ section.settings.skill_1_label }}</dt>
                <dd class="batlle-biography__skill-value">{{ section.settings.skill_1_value }}</dd>
              </div>
            {%- endif -%}
            {%- if section.settings.skill_2_value != blank -%}
              <div>
                <dt class="batlle-biography__skill-label">{{ section.settings.skill_2_label }}</dt>
                <dd class="batlle-biography__skill-value">{{ section.settings.skill_2_value }}</dd>
              </div>
            {%- endif -%}
            {%- if section.settings.skill_3_value != blank -%}
              <div>
                <dt class="batlle-biography__skill-label">{{ section.settings.skill_3_label }}</dt>
                <dd class="batlle-biography__skill-value">{{ section.settings.skill_3_value }}</dd>
              </div>
            {%- endif -%}
          </dl>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "t:sections.batlle-biography.name",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "section",
  "disabled_on": {
    "groups": ["header", "footer"]
  },
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "portrait",
      "label": "t:sections.batlle-biography.settings.portrait.label"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "name_badge",
      "default": "Louise",
      "label": "t:sections.batlle-biography.settings.name_badge.label"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "supertitle",
      "default": "La créatrice · Parcours",
      "label": "t:sections.batlle-biography.settings.supertitle.label"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "title",
      "default": "<p>Louise, <em>violoniste</em> et couturière.</p>",
      "label": "t:sections.batlle-biography.settings.title.label"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "body",
      "default": "<p>Née à Toulouse, je grandis entre les cordes du violon et les chutes de tissu. Très tôt, la musique et la couture me semblent répondre à la même exigence : la précision du geste au service de l'émotion.</p><p>Je me forme à l'<strong>Institut Français de la Mode</strong> puis à l'<strong>AICP</strong> — deux écoles réputées pour leur technicité et leur approche radicale de la coupe. J'y apprends le flou, le tailleur et le corset, les trois langues de la couture.</p><p>Avec Batlle, je réinterprète les histoires anciennes — chevaleresses, sorcières, mystiques, héroïnes oubliées — pour habiller les femmes d'aujourd'hui.</p>",
      "label": "t:sections.batlle-biography.settings.body.label"
    },
    {
      "type": "color_scheme",
      "id": "color_scheme",
      "default": "scheme-1",
      "label": "t:sections.all.colors.label"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Compétences"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "skill_1_label",
      "default": "Flou",
      "label": "t:sections.batlle-biography.settings.skill_1_label.label"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "skill_1_value",
      "default": "Drapé",
      "label": "t:sections.batlle-biography.settings.skill_1_value.label"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "skill_2_label",
      "default": "Tailleur",
      "label": "t:sections.batlle-biography.settings.skill_2_label.label"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "skill_2_value",
      "default": "Coupe · Structure",
      "label": "t:sections.batlle-biography.settings.skill_2_value.label"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "skill_3_label",
      "default": "Corset",
      "label": "t:sections.batlle-biography.settings.skill_3_label.label"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "skill_3_value",
      "default": "Architecture du corps",
      "label": "t:sections.batlle-biography.settings.skill_3_value.label"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "t:sections.batlle-biography.presets.name"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
